{"word":"ἰυγμός","slug":"ἰυγμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰυγμός</b></el> <el>(ἰυγμός,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἰύζω'><el>ἰύζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a shouting, shout of joy</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a cry of pain, shriek</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}